# Help + AI Reference Sync

When implementing or changing user-facing features, always update docs in the same task.

## Required updates

- Update `src/pages/HelpPage.tsx` for any new or changed workflows.
- Update `src/services/helpChatService.ts` system context so AI guidance matches current UI/flows.

## Minimum content expectations

- Add or adjust FAQ entries when behavior changes.
- Update Feature descriptions when controls, labels, or toolbar sections change.
- Add/refresh "What's New" items for notable shipped features.

## Quality guardrails

- Never document menus/buttons that do not exist.
- Use current labels as shown in the UI.
- Keep instructions task-oriented and concise.
